Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.98,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无 风 日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快递
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 请在这里签名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 工作方面缺不缺人手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说想找个工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你就是大家说的那个宇宙少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找工作啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月正好有个人退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经雇了新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓鱼的活儿肯定找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为错过了洋流交汇带 最近一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.18,tips,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：暖流与寒流的交汇地带往往渔业资源丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到忙起来的时候 我会找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正忙着整理账单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这活外行也干不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点倒是有了眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还要过三天才能到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 害你期待了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该去送快递了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我试着自己找看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好 很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微往上点 往上点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 都说是最上面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 左边  那边往左
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 做不来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的适用条件居然如此严格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 数据库有更新吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍未找到适合贵官从事的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团的推进装置正在逐一停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那里傻站着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转换一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 舰团停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没风了啦 没风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 集合了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肉够大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够大吃一顿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你搞得到手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在搞派对没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易碰到无风日 应该有很多修理工作要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混到我这个位置 手下干活的人要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是弗兰基的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电源关掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已经确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 派对会场在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 刚刚那是皮尼欧的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 因为无风日风平浪静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会选在这样的日子里维修船舶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团会离开银河道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力也会中断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有维修人员才能工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人则全都放假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景不赖吧 这可是绝佳位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 无风的海面就是这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱雅 梅露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那里好像不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别穿那件老土的衣服了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 身材挺棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔德姆医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就打扰一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是费了好大劲才搞到的好肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力还没恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 破废铁 你不能想点办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象焚化完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要交给你去办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去铁匠婆婆那里一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你去最合适
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是只有你才能做到的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你要让雷德到那种地方去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然 谁让他浪费掉了一盘子的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PartB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是背后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德他不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然痒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下吃完烤肉又要发胖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么「又要」啊 梅露蒂你根本不用担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有自己的标准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不少男生喜欢肉感的女生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会这点的话可是要吃苦头的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还 还是应该运动一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起重机塔的喷水器你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然电力恢复了 那东西却没动静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 又坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用冲浪风筝上去开启水泵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.90,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,650)}Surf Kite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我接下来要参加烤肉派对的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 那么拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:12:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来比试一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 我可不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就不用担心发胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何在积极摄取食物的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又执着于维持体型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的少女心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…破废铁 你很黑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 小弟弟你一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这脸蛋长得真甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好嫩的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终点是起重机塔的顶端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 升空的方法不要那么乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,询问采取该行动的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的绞盘你还修不修了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会修的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是工作忙得很吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意这些小事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起吃吧 马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们这里工作怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉发生了紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对那家伙来说也算是有意义的社会实践
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机表示同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 你在那做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这身打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚在监督船底的检修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这里的电力什么时候才会恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作没法按时完成 可能要停到傍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身泳衣好大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人不用承担业绩指标的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事 我到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定能成为我们店的头牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 臀部曲线也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体力也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 总是艾米占甜头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比赛就是比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你怎么会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我接着工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着这条路走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是场不错的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就可以放开大吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,询问采取该行动的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 询问采取该行动的必要性…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人 你想要这个做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样就能解决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是某种零件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要回到那里去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 谁干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把派对的事到处提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 宇宙少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有盐总觉得不够味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 谁想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然婆婆的酱汁最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 不快吃就没了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也尝尝自己劳动的结晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 起风了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 干活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 毕竟你是途中才来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这场派对明明是为你准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雷德一直没有找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧为了替你打气才特意安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为大家努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 为大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有你 大家才吃到了美味的烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会陪你一起去找工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道雷德哥哥适合什么工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还是体力活吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这种地方偷懒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这可是名正言顺的工…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,询问采取该行动的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.07,0:22:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 询问采取该行…

